This directory stores the serialized FAISS index and chunk metadata files
produced by the offline build_index.py script. These files are loaded by the
retriever at gateway startup.

Expected files after a successful index build:
  - faiss_index.bin       — Serialized FAISS HNSW index (~10-50 MB)
  - chunk_metadata.json   — Mapping from vector ID to chunk object (~5-20 MB)
  - index_manifest.json   — Build metadata (timestamp, params, chunk count)

These files are NOT committed to git (too large). They are built on the
development machine and deployed to the gateway via rsync or manual copy.
